<div style="padding-left:10px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:2px; font-size:100%">
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/Faali:Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png/250px-Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png" decoding="async" width="250" height="158" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png/330px-Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png/500px-Administration_block_of_Bolgatanga_Technical_University.png 2x" data-file-width="500" data-file-height="316"></a><figcaption>Districts of the Upper East Region</figcaption></figure>
<b><a href="/wiki/Bolgatanga_Regional_Hospital" title="Bolgatanga Regional Hospital">Bolgatanga Regional Hospital</a></b> de la Gɔmena Asibetin kãtɛ mboi Bɔlega Zaarɛ, timbila diyima m boi Gaana wa saazuo bɔba so'olum (Upper East Region). Asibetin la de la Bɔlega za'a asibetin kãtɛ. Bala la nɛra san bi'ira gee kiŋɛ asibetin bibesi la puan ti dɔgeta duma la baŋɛ ti ba ta'am tibɛ, ba ni ta'asɛ e basɛ la bilam. Bala la nɛreba zo'e zo'e yi'iri di la dɔgekatin...<a href="/wiki/Bolgatanga_Regional_Hospital" title="Bolgatanga Regional Hospital">Kãalɛ zo'e zo'e</a><div align="right" style="font-size:95%;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipiidiya:Featured_Articles&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Wikipiidiya:Featured Articles (pɛgerɛ la ka boe)">Zina Daarɛ Wa garɛ</a></div></div>
<div style="text-align:left; position:relative; left:4px; top:2px; margin:0;">
<p><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png" decoding="async" width="350" height="25" class="mw-file-element" data-file-width="350" data-file-height="25"></span></span>

<div style="position:absolute; left:40px; top:-5px;"><div style="font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em;">Zina Gɔŋɔ La Ama</div></div></div>
<div style="padding-left:10px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:2px; font-size:100%">
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/Faali:Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg/250px-Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="187" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg/330px-Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg/500px-Upper_East_Fork_Patrol_Cabin.jpg 2x" data-file-width="2560" data-file-height="1920"></a><figcaption>Bolgatanga Senior High School</figcaption></figure>
<b>Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS)</b> bo la <a href="/wiki/Upper_East_Region" title="Upper East Region">Upper East Region</a>, Ghana. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la deti ti ba wi'ira ti 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS)' la, dela kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ wia daana ti a bɔna upper east. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la yuum pɔsɛ la '15 October, 1970'. Sukuu la yuum pɔsɛ mɛ la kɔma piyopɔi la ba nuu. Pa'aleba yuum dela pia la ayima deti Mr. Bayala C. J. Yibrul dɛna sukuu la zuo daana 'first Heamaster'.     Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS) bo la Upper East Region, Ghana. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la deti ti ba wi'ira ti 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS)' la, dela kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ wia daana ti a bɔna upper east. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la yuum pɔsɛ la '15 October, 1970'. Sukuu la yuum pɔsɛ mɛ la kɔma piyopɔi la ba nuu. Pa'aleba yuum dela pia la ayima deti Mr. Bayala C. J. Yibrul dɛna sukuu la zuo daana 'first Heamaster'. Pa'aleba sɛba n yuum kiŋɛ sukuu ba'asɛ dee bɔna bini pa'ala dela batã deti sɛba n yuum suŋeri ba me nyaa dɛna...Kãalɛ zo'e zo'e]]

    Fum Mi Ti ....?
    • Fathia Nkrumah zou la Zeitoun, ende ziɛn mbo Cairo.Fathia yuun dela la Coptic Egyptian ge dɛna Gãana wia kuka zuo daana pɔga (first president Kwame Nkrumah) Fathia Nkrumah buuri yuun dela Coptic Christian duma. Ka mɛ yuun dela ka sɔ/ ba bi kiima. Ka sɔ/ba la yuun te'ele ki la kalam de gee la ka Ma ma'a ti ka yuum bisera n ti ka yuun ta zo'e kutɛ.
    • Ghana Gaana dela suma'asum tiŋa bɔna Afirika wa la timpaberɛ wa za'an waabi puan. Gaana tiŋa wa yuum bo la solemiisi nu'usi ti ba sɔna tiŋa bisera. La yuum ta paɛ la saŋa ti Gaana nɛreba yuum waɛ isege ze'ele ba nama Zuo zɛbɛ nyaŋɛ solemiisi la dee nyaa to'e tiŋa ti la nyaa dɛna Gaana duma meŋa tiŋa ti ba sɔna bisera. Ba yuum nyaŋɛ zɛbɛ to'e tiŋa wa la 1957?
    • Did You Know/Upper East Region Upper East tinkatɛ de la Bɔlegataŋa. Bɔlegataŋa boi la Gaana saazuo bɔba. Bɔlegataŋa tiŋa la pu la pia la anuu dee ti ba wi'ira ba ti 'districts' la. Bɔlegataŋa miŋa dɛna ba tinkatɛ dee kelum bɔna tiŋasuka.?
    • Ghana Senior High School (GHANASCO) nyɛla bi’kura karim zɔŋ shɛli din be Tamali Northern Region, Ghana tiŋgban ni ka n-nyɛ yuun' pihi yɔbu?

Bolgatanga Regional Hospital de la Gɔmena Asibetin kãtɛ mboi Bɔlega Zaarɛ, timbila diyima m boi Gaana wa saazuo bɔba so'olum (Upper East Region). Asibetin la de la Bɔlega za'a asibetin kãtɛ. Bala la nɛra san bi'ira gee kiŋɛ asibetin bibesi la puan ti dɔgeta duma la baŋɛ ti ba ta'am tibɛ, ba ni ta'asɛ e basɛ la bilam. Bala la nɛreba zo'e zo'e yi'iri di la dɔgekatin...Kãalɛ zo'e zo'e
Zina Daarɛ Wa garɛ

Zina Gɔŋɔ La Ama
Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS) bo la Upper East Region, Ghana. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la deti ti ba wi'ira ti 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS)' la, dela kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ wia daana ti a bɔna upper east. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la yuum pɔsɛ la '15 October, 1970'. Sukuu la yuum pɔsɛ mɛ la kɔma piyopɔi la ba nuu. Pa'aleba yuum dela pia la ayima deti Mr. Bayala C. J. Yibrul dɛna sukuu la zuo daana 'first Heamaster'. Pa'aleba sɛba n yuum kiŋɛ sukuu ba'asɛ dee bɔna bini pa'ala dela batã deti sɛba n yuum suŋeri ba me nyaa dɛna banii.[[Bolgatanga Senior High School|......Kãalɛ zo'e zo'e]]
Zina Daarɛ Wa garɛ

Fum Mi Ti ....?
  • Fathia Nkrumah zou la Zeitoun, ende ziɛn mbo Cairo.Fathia yuun dela la Coptic Egyptian ge dɛna Gãana wia kuka zuo daana pɔga (first president Kwame Nkrumah) Fathia Nkrumah buuri yuun dela Coptic Christian duma. Ka mɛ yuun dela ka sɔ/ ba bi kiima. Ka sɔ/ba la yuun te'ele ki la kalam de gee la ka Ma ma'a ti ka yuum bisera n ti ka yuun ta zo'e kutɛ.
  • Ghana Gaana dela suma'asum tiŋa bɔna Afirika wa la timpaberɛ wa za'an waabi puan. Gaana tiŋa wa yuum bo la solemiisi nu'usi ti ba sɔna tiŋa bisera. La yuum ta paɛ la saŋa ti Gaana nɛreba yuum waɛ isege ze'ele ba nama Zuo zɛbɛ nyaŋɛ solemiisi la dee nyaa to'e tiŋa ti la nyaa dɛna Gaana duma meŋa tiŋa ti ba sɔna bisera. Ba yuum nyaŋɛ zɛbɛ to'e tiŋa wa la 1957?
  • Did You Know/Upper East Region Upper East tinkatɛ de la Bɔlegataŋa. Bɔlegataŋa boi la Gaana saazuo bɔba. Bɔlegataŋa tiŋa la pu la pia la anuu dee ti ba wi'ira ba ti 'districts' la. Bɔlegataŋa miŋa dɛna ba tinkatɛ dee kelum bɔna tiŋasuka.?
  • Ghana Senior High School (GHANASCO) nyɛla bi’kura karim zɔŋ shɛli din be Tamali Northern Region, Ghana tiŋgban ni ka n-nyɛ yuun' pihi yɔbu?
    Zina Daarɛ Wa garɛ

Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la deti ti ba wi'ira ti 'Bolgatanga Senior High School (BIG BOSS)' la, dela kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ wia daana ti a bɔna upper east. Bɔlegataŋa kɔmbibesi sukuu katɛ la yuum pɔsɛ la '15 October, 1970'. Sukuu la yuum pɔsɛ mɛ la kɔma piyopɔi la ba nuu. Pa'aleba yuum dela pia la ayima deti Mr. Bayala C. J. Yibrul dɛna sukuu la zuo daana 'first Heamaster'. Pa'aleba sɛba n yuum kiŋɛ sukuu ba'asɛ dee bɔna bini pa'ala dela batã deti sɛba n yuum suŋeri ba me nyaa dɛna banii.[[Bolgatanga Senior High School|......Kãalɛ zo'e zo'e]]Zina Daarɛ Wa garɛ

Jerry John Rawlings 
Fathia Nkrumah zou la Zeitoun, ende ziɛn mbo Cairo.Fathia yuun dela la Coptic Egyptian ge dɛna Gãana wia kuka zuo daana pɔga (first president Kwame Nkrumah) Fathia Nkrumah buuri yuun dela Coptic Christian duma. Ka mɛ yuun dela ka sɔ/ ba bi kiima. Ka sɔ/ba la yuun te'ele ki la kalam de gee la ka Ma ma'a ti ka yuum bisera n ti ka yuun ta zo'e kutɛ.
Ghana Gaana dela suma'asum tiŋa bɔna Afirika wa la timpaberɛ wa za'an waabi puan. Gaana tiŋa wa yuum bo la solemiisi nu'usi ti ba sɔna tiŋa bisera. La yuum ta paɛ la saŋa ti Gaana nɛreba yuum waɛ isege ze'ele ba nama Zuo zɛbɛ nyaŋɛ solemiisi la dee nyaa to'e tiŋa ti la nyaa dɛna Gaana duma meŋa tiŋa ti ba sɔna bisera. Ba yuum nyaŋɛ zɛbɛ to'e tiŋa wa la 1957?
